      <title>Desmarais 的 Power Sustainable 放弃中国股票策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/desmarais-power-sustainable-gives-up-on-china-equities-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Power Sustainable 是一家专注于气候的公司，由蒙特利尔亿万富翁 Desmarais 家族控制，该公司正在关闭其在中国的投资管理业务，并逐步取消其在中国的公开股票战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/desmarais-power-sustainable-gives-up-on-china-equities-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
